{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Game Introduction</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a Rogue-like game with a combination of JRPG, auto chess, and galgame elements. Players can choose from two different female protagonists to embark on a unique adventure. Additionally, players can recruit followers, strategize their formations, and develop their town!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After centuries since the last war, Geoffrey of the Black God Cult, who was defeated in the previous events, did not die. However, the power of the demons was weakened, and they all lurked within the human world. Geoffrey and the demon clan began to execute new plans to break the seal, and a conspiracy was brewing in the shadows... </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game features dozens of minion cards, each with unique skills and effects, showcasing their individual characteristics. Every minion possesses distinct racial effects that, when activated, enhance different racial attributes, making battles significantly more manageable.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are four main female protagonists in the game, each forming diverse and engaging storylines. Try starting the game with different protagonists for varied experiences.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game incorporates mild Rogue elements, including diverse combinations of minions, equipment, and artifacts. Additionally, players can explore various random events within the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Towns play a crucial role in the game. By interacting with NPCs and upgrading the town, players can significantly enhance the freshness of gameplay.</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Fenrir","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2688680/9efcf90dad814eca169709b4f7c3f78bea4576f8.jpg"},{"name":"Breaking Dawn","path":"https://cdn.akamai.ste